        <txttip left="68" top="320" right="329" bottom="484" content="IP Address Planning&#x0D;&#x0A;VLAN 10: 192.168.1.0/25&#x0D;&#x0A;  PC1: 192.168.1.1/25&#x0D;&#x0A;  PC3: 192.168.1.3/25&#x0D;&#x0A;&#x0D;&#x0A;VLAN 20: 192.168.1.128/25&#x0D;&#x0A;  PC2: 192.168.1.129/25&#x0D;&#x0A;  PC4: 192.168.1.130/25" fontname="Consolas" fontstyle="0" editsize="130" txtcolor="-16777216" txtbkcolor="-4144960" charset="1" />
        <txttip left="406" top="323" right="824" bottom="487" content="Interface   Type    PVID   Permitted VLANs&#x0D;&#x0A;SW1-G0/0/1  Access  10     -&#x0D;&#x0A;SW1-G0/0/2  Access  20     -&#x0D;&#x0A;SW1-G0/0/3  Trunk   1      1,10,20&#x0D;&#x0A;&#x0D;&#x0A;SW2-G0/0/1  Access  10     -&#x0D;&#x0A;SW2-G0/0/2  Access  20     -&#x0D;&#x0A;SW2-G0/0/3  Trunk   1      1,10,20" fontname="Consolas" fontstyle="0" editsize="130" txtcolor="-16777216" txtbkcolor="-4144960" charset="1" />
        <txttip left="11" top="494" right="1248" bottom="683" content="Requirements:&#x0D;&#x0A;1. Configure device names and IP addresses for each device&#x0D;&#x0A;2. Configure IP addresses and VLANs according to the above reference tables.&#x0D;&#x0A;3. Using ping utility, test connectivity between each device to each other device. Which Computers can communicate? Why not the others?&#x0D;&#x0A;4. Capture ping(ICMP) frames at G0/0/1 of SW1 and G0/0/3 of SW1. Through WireShark, compare the captured frame encapsulations.&#x0D;&#x0A;   Be sure to run a ping from PC1 to PC3 to capture frames. What&apos;s the difference between the frame encapsulations?&#x0D;&#x0A; Answer: the different is at second frame which are showing the are some different &#x0D;&#x0A;5. Save your configurations on all devices and save the topology as &apos;Name-UserID-VLANlab1&apos;&#x0D;&#x0A;&#x0D;&#x0A;NOTE: Please save your captures and add them to your zipped folder. They should be submitted together with the Lab." fontname="Consolas" fontstyle="0" editsize="120" txtcolor="-16777216" txtbkcolor="-4144960" charset="1" />
        <txttip left="624" top="263" right="704" bottom="309" content="Finance&#x0D;&#x0A;VLAN 10" fontname="Consolas" fontstyle="0" editsize="140" txtcolor="-16777216" txtbkcolor="-1" charset="1" />
